casebody.data:
No. 109,

Orig.

Oklahoma et al. v. New Mexico. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 493 U. S. 929.]

Motion of the Special Master for allowance of compensation and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded $61,292.54 for the period September 1, 1989, through January 31, 1990, one-third to be paid by each party.
